urnal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Sustainabledevelopment.un.org&amp;rft.atitle=Press+release+%E2%80%93+UN+General+Assembly%E2%80%99s+Open+Working+Group+proposes+sustainable+development+goals&amp;rft.date=2014-07-19&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fsustainabledevelopment.un.org%2Fcontent%2Fdocuments%2F4538pressowg13.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASustainable+Development+Goal+6\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-SDG6_targets-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-SDG6_targets_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-SDG6_targets_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-SDG6_targets_4-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.undp.org/content/undp/en/home/sustainable-development-goals/goal-6-clean-water-and-sanitation/targets/\">\"Goal 6 Targets\"</a>. <i>United Nations Development Programme</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">16 November</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=United+Nations+Development+Programme&amp;rft.atitle=Goal+6+Targets&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.undp.org%2Fcontent%2Fundp%2Fen%2Fhome%2Fsustainable-development-goals%2Fgoal-6-clean-water-and-sanitation%2Ftargets%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASustainable+Development+Goal+6\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-:12-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-:12_5-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:12_5-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sustainabledevelopmen